  "body": "\r\n### Description\r\n\r\n*Type*: Bug\r\n\r\nWhen logging out and logging back in the mobile application, after clicking wallet the Syncing message displays and the spinning icon does not stop spinning\r\n\r\n#### Expected behavior\r\nIf a network issue is causing this to occur there should be a timeout and a timeout error should be displayed \r\n\r\n#### Actual behavior\r\nSyncing message and spinning icon displays and does not time out\r\n### Reproduction\r\nLoad the application\r\nLog out of the app\r\nLogin to the application\r\nClick the Wallet icon\r\n\r\nStatus version:0.9.12(1557.321)\r\nDevice:iphone7\r\nVersion:10.3.3\r\nOS:iOS\r\n\r\n![loadingicon](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/9959969/33869258-687a7cba-decd-11e7-925e-7f60fc258633.PNG)\r\n",
